WEBVTT

00:53.595 --> 00:54.971
Don't do it, Jun-hui--

01:10.278 --> 01:12.405
- Are you okay?
- My gosh.

01:12.489 --> 01:14.282
See? I told you.

01:14.365 --> 01:16.409
Those two are a couple.

01:16.493 --> 01:18.495
Why am I being treated like a lunatic?

01:18.578 --> 01:20.330
I'm going to sue all of you.

01:20.413 --> 01:22.540
Please be quiet and sit down.

01:22.624 --> 01:23.833
Okay? Sit down.

01:33.384 --> 01:34.302
Jin-a.

01:38.431 --> 01:39.265
Hey.

01:40.350 --> 01:42.644
- Let's talk later.
- Why later?

01:42.852 --> 01:44.103
Gyu-min!

01:44.187 --> 01:45.104
Mom.

01:45.355 --> 01:47.774
My goodness, Gyu-min. What happened?

01:48.274 --> 01:50.985
Who did this? Who did this to you?

01:53.238 --> 01:55.281
Wait, aren't you Jin-a?

01:55.698 --> 01:56.825
Hello.

01:57.700 --> 01:58.618
Did you two fight?

02:00.161 --> 02:01.079
I'm sorry.

02:01.162 --> 02:03.289
You're unbelievable.

02:03.456 --> 02:06.793
How could you beat a guy up like this?

02:07.168 --> 02:08.461
My sister's the victim.

02:09.504 --> 02:10.713
You can talk things out later.

02:10.922 --> 02:13.299
First, I need to talk to your guardians.
Are you his guardian?

02:13.800 --> 02:14.884
Yes.

02:15.260 --> 02:16.719
Who's her guardian?

02:22.725 --> 02:23.768
Please show me your IDs.

02:32.777 --> 02:34.946
You kept denying it. Have some shame.

02:41.870 --> 02:44.747
EPISODE 7

02:50.628 --> 02:51.713
Get in.

02:58.428 --> 03:00.889
Jin-a, I need to have a word with you.

03:01.431 --> 03:03.766
We just settled everything.
What else is there to talk about?

03:04.142 --> 03:05.602
You can talk to me if you need to.

03:06.311 --> 03:07.645
Who are you to meddle in?

03:09.105 --> 03:11.024
Then I will go ahead
and have a word with your son

03:11.149 --> 03:12.817
while you talk to my sister, all right?

03:12.901 --> 03:15.653
- What did you just say?
- Do you expect me to be polite to you?

03:15.737 --> 03:16.863
Seung-ho, enough.

03:17.947 --> 03:19.949
You should just leave.

03:21.075 --> 03:22.327
And who are you?

03:24.579 --> 03:25.914
Is this guy your brother too?

03:28.541 --> 03:29.584
I'm...

03:30.293 --> 03:33.296
- I'm her brother's--
- He's my boyfriend.

05:54.020 --> 05:54.896
Aren't you coming in?

05:58.274 --> 05:59.484
Why are you standing there?

05:59.650 --> 06:00.902
Come on. Let's go in.

06:03.446 --> 06:06.074
- Gosh, seriously.
- I'm sorry, Seung-ho.

06:06.365 --> 06:08.659
Hey, Jin-a! Wait!

10:11.485 --> 10:13.404
You don't seem like you are hungover.

10:13.487 --> 10:15.031
Didn't you stay out late?

10:15.531 --> 10:17.533
- You didn't drink last night?
- No.

10:17.617 --> 10:19.410
Then what did you
and Gyeong-seon do all night?

10:23.873 --> 10:26.375
Oh, right. Why didn't you tell me
that Jun-hui was the one

10:26.459 --> 10:28.669
who gave you a ride
when you went on the business trip?

10:32.923 --> 10:33.924
Answer me.

10:34.258 --> 10:36.469
My gosh, Seung-ho. Are you leaving now?

10:36.969 --> 10:38.929
Seung-ho, wait.

10:53.944 --> 10:55.404
I will talk to Seung-ho.

10:58.199 --> 10:59.241
Then what?

11:00.284 --> 11:02.453
Are we going to take turns

11:02.578 --> 11:04.622
to explain ourselves to everyone?

11:06.957 --> 11:08.626
Why does it have to be so complicated?

11:09.919 --> 11:11.128
Are you worth all this trouble?

11:12.129 --> 11:13.589
Are you blaming everything on me now?

11:16.133 --> 11:19.637
It's simple. Just like any other couple,
we met and started dating.

11:20.137 --> 11:21.305
There's nothing wrong with it.

11:23.933 --> 11:25.601
Putting it that way

11:26.394 --> 11:28.771
makes it sound like
it's not a big deal at all.

11:29.271 --> 11:30.606
It's true though.

11:32.691 --> 11:34.777
But why do I find it so hard already?

11:35.736 --> 11:38.030
I mean, Seung-ho is the only one
who knows about us now.

11:41.200 --> 11:43.369
Try not to stress over it.
I'll take all the blame.

11:45.329 --> 11:46.997
I won't let them blame you for everything.

11:48.207 --> 11:51.085
All right,
then you take the bullet for me.

11:51.585 --> 11:53.337
Goodness.

11:55.965 --> 11:58.676
Don't worry. I'll be a better boyfriend.

12:00.219 --> 12:02.555
You'd better. I'll punch you
if you don't keep your word.

12:32.001 --> 12:33.419
Do you see anything up there?

12:36.755 --> 12:39.008
I don't see anything.

12:39.508 --> 12:40.885
What are you looking at?

12:42.344 --> 12:44.597
I can't see anything.

12:52.480 --> 12:54.565
I don't see any flaws.

12:54.648 --> 12:56.817
The head office might think
I was too lenient with you.

12:57.359 --> 12:58.444
Because you want my help?

13:03.032 --> 13:04.200
Maybe you can actually help me

13:04.283 --> 13:06.952
and give me a reason
to be lenient with you.

13:07.077 --> 13:09.413
I'll try to leave the store messy
next time you come.

13:11.582 --> 13:12.917
Did you have fun in Gangwon-do?

13:13.918 --> 13:14.960
You went there with Jin-a.

13:15.127 --> 13:17.463
I heard Ms. Geum went there, too.

13:18.714 --> 13:19.924
Didn't you go?

13:21.425 --> 13:23.552
This is my first time hearing about it.

13:31.018 --> 13:33.479
Did you go to Gangwon-do with Jin-a?

13:37.191 --> 13:40.277
MS. TAMBOURINE

13:48.869 --> 13:50.037
What is going on?

13:55.793 --> 13:57.044
KIM SEUNG-CHEOL

14:14.061 --> 14:16.438
Hello, this is Geum Bo-ra.

14:18.440 --> 14:20.442
It's Geum Bo-ra.

14:23.612 --> 14:25.072
Geum Bo-ra.

14:25.155 --> 14:28.868
Yes, Ms. Geum. How can I help you?

14:31.912 --> 14:33.289
Jun-hui?

14:36.292 --> 14:37.126
Sure.

14:38.711 --> 14:39.879
Jun-hui.

14:40.796 --> 14:41.964
It's Ms. Geum.

14:42.298 --> 14:43.340
For me?

14:45.801 --> 14:46.844
Hello?

14:48.137 --> 14:49.179
Yes.

14:52.975 --> 14:54.018
Yes.

14:57.187 --> 14:59.648
I really do owe you a meal.

15:02.651 --> 15:05.613
I'll text you my number.
You can call me directly next time.

15:06.113 --> 15:07.323
What's going on?

15:08.073 --> 15:09.116
Yes.

15:10.075 --> 15:11.452
Of course.

15:11.702 --> 15:14.079
I'm free whenever, so make time for me.

15:15.623 --> 15:16.624
Okay.

15:17.625 --> 15:19.627
Hey. Is...

15:20.085 --> 15:21.795
Is she the one?

15:22.796 --> 15:24.506
It was her, not a married woman?

15:25.132 --> 15:27.009
Stop talking nonsense.

15:28.719 --> 15:29.637
Jun-hui.

15:32.014 --> 15:33.974
You finally came around.

15:34.683 --> 15:35.684
Good job.

15:36.226 --> 15:38.020
- Hey, wait.
- Good.

15:38.103 --> 15:41.565
I'll take good care of Se-yeong.

15:43.776 --> 15:44.777
What?

15:46.779 --> 15:47.821
I got this.

15:51.325 --> 15:53.118
Gosh, that little punk.

15:57.164 --> 15:58.457
Here's your coffee.

15:59.583 --> 16:01.543
They did go to Gangwon-do.

16:01.961 --> 16:03.712
That's so ridiculous.

16:04.546 --> 16:06.131
Why did they leave me out?

16:06.215 --> 16:08.968
Maybe you have been
leaving them out in the cold.

16:09.051 --> 16:10.719
No way.

16:11.095 --> 16:14.974
Maybe Jin-a is, but Bo-ra is not the type
to go on a trip with coworkers.

16:17.101 --> 16:20.562
Have Jun-hui ever mentioned her to you?

16:20.854 --> 16:23.315
Her name is Geum Bo-ra,
and she's one of my colleagues.

16:23.399 --> 16:26.276
He never talks about girls to me.

16:26.860 --> 16:29.113
Why? Is there something going on
between the two?

16:29.279 --> 16:32.533
- Not exactly.
- Thank you.

16:32.741 --> 16:35.661
But they seem close.

16:36.245 --> 16:39.081
That's possible
if she's Jin-a's colleague.

16:41.125 --> 16:42.167
Right.

16:43.961 --> 16:44.962
Well...

16:45.838 --> 16:48.007
Do you know what type of woman

16:48.132 --> 16:50.801
Jun-hui likes?

16:52.302 --> 16:54.805
Are you asking me if you are his type?

16:57.933 --> 16:59.435
Yes, that's what I really want to know.

17:01.228 --> 17:03.605
What kind of family does
Ms. Geum come from?

17:04.148 --> 17:05.232
Her family?

17:05.315 --> 17:06.859
Is it a prestigious family?

17:06.984 --> 17:08.569
It has to be above average.

17:08.652 --> 17:11.780
The more reputable, the better.

17:12.156 --> 17:15.534
It's what our parents want dearly.

17:19.038 --> 17:21.457
Jun-hui isn't an easy target, is he?

17:22.541 --> 17:24.710
Ma'am, for this level of damage,

17:24.793 --> 17:26.837
buying a new phone would cost you less

17:26.920 --> 17:28.881
than getting it repaired.

17:28.964 --> 17:31.592
Yes, I thought so.
I did want to change my phone.

17:31.675 --> 17:33.635
- In that case...
- Yes.

17:34.094 --> 17:36.889
This phone is
under Mr. Lee Gyu-min's name.

17:37.556 --> 17:38.932
- Yes.
- Is he a family member?

17:39.308 --> 17:40.267
No.

17:42.144 --> 17:44.146
Under the current law,

17:44.563 --> 17:47.066
the account holder
has to be here in person.

17:49.151 --> 17:51.570
What if he can't be here in person?

17:52.154 --> 17:53.947
In that case, you can't change your phone.

17:55.240 --> 17:59.244
Even though I have been paying the bill
and the installment payments?

17:59.328 --> 18:00.913
That doesn't matter.

18:02.831 --> 18:07.586
Do you mean I can't change
my phone on my own?

18:07.795 --> 18:10.130
Not under the current law.

18:23.060 --> 18:24.394
Why didn't you pick up the phone?

18:25.771 --> 18:26.897
Don't talk about phones.

18:26.980 --> 18:28.732
You still have to listen to me.

18:28.816 --> 18:29.691
What?

18:32.945 --> 18:35.697
Wait, what? What is this about?

18:43.122 --> 18:46.125
You'd better be good to me
now that I have something on you.

18:46.625 --> 18:48.293
I don't think being good to you is enough.

18:48.377 --> 18:51.046
I'd better pledge my life to you.

18:51.380 --> 18:52.840
Thanks anyway.

18:53.632 --> 18:55.217
You know that I normally don't care

18:55.300 --> 18:57.845
- about other people's businesses.
- I do.

18:57.928 --> 19:01.974
But no matter how hard I think about it,
I just can't understand you two.

19:02.474 --> 19:04.226
Why can't you openly date him?

19:05.060 --> 19:08.105
Frankly speaking, he's not your own
brother and neither of you are married.

19:08.188 --> 19:09.231
What's the problem?

19:10.858 --> 19:13.402
Let's just say
I'm taking moral responsibility.

19:14.862 --> 19:16.071
Am I supposed to laugh at that?

19:16.405 --> 19:18.365
I guess that's better than crying over it.

19:19.032 --> 19:20.033
Gosh.

19:20.576 --> 19:22.077
Anyhow...

19:23.120 --> 19:26.331
You're saying that he's someone
who's worth all this trouble, right?

19:27.499 --> 19:28.584
Is he that great?

19:29.334 --> 19:31.253
Yes, he's greater than great.

19:32.796 --> 19:34.464
You just don't know when to stop, do you?

19:34.715 --> 19:36.008
- To be honest...
- What?

19:37.217 --> 19:38.760
You know,

19:39.303 --> 19:41.180
every time I see him,

19:41.263 --> 19:43.265
my heart just races.

19:44.683 --> 19:47.269
And I get that warm fuzzy feeling

19:47.394 --> 19:49.021
right inside here.

19:49.104 --> 19:51.190
- Have you ever felt that way?
- Let's see. You must have

19:51.273 --> 19:52.357
a problem with your heart.

19:52.482 --> 19:54.610
Look at you getting all mushy.

19:54.818 --> 19:55.861
Gosh.

19:56.361 --> 19:58.113
I never knew
that I would ever be involved in

19:58.197 --> 19:59.740
someone's relationship like this.

20:00.157 --> 20:04.828
I never thought that I would ever
talk about something like this with you.

20:06.246 --> 20:08.332
Life is so unpredictable, you know.

20:08.498 --> 20:11.501
Now that we are in it together,
can I borrow your phone?

20:14.296 --> 20:15.297
Here.

20:15.881 --> 20:17.633
Gosh.

20:19.134 --> 20:20.385
Do you like him that much?

20:24.431 --> 20:28.018
- "Ms. Tambourine's boyfriend"?
- I'll change it. I was going to change it.

20:29.019 --> 20:30.103
Change it.

20:30.270 --> 20:32.105
I will change it.

20:43.408 --> 20:45.410
I'm not Ms. Geum.

20:45.661 --> 20:47.079
Guess who I am.

20:48.455 --> 20:50.374
Yes, it's Jin-a.

20:51.541 --> 20:52.542
I'm sorry.

20:53.585 --> 20:56.088
- You're working? Okay.
- I'm leaving.

21:04.888 --> 21:07.349
Let's go get a new phone after the meal.

21:11.103 --> 21:13.188
I can wait few more days.

21:13.897 --> 21:16.775
I don't really need it
since I'm always at the store.

21:17.109 --> 21:19.027
It's nice
that I don't have to answer crank calls.

21:20.320 --> 21:22.364
- Then what about me?
- What?

21:25.450 --> 21:27.035
We see each other almost every day.

21:27.119 --> 21:28.787
We can set up a time to meet
the day before.

21:30.622 --> 21:32.541
What if something comes up
or we miss each other?

21:33.208 --> 21:34.084
It's too inconvenient.

21:35.502 --> 21:36.878
Okay, I'll buy one.

21:37.504 --> 21:38.797
I'll go with you and buy you one.

21:39.589 --> 21:42.509
No, don't bother. I can get it myself.

21:55.105 --> 21:56.148
How about a glass of wine?

21:57.399 --> 22:00.402
Right, you have to pull
an all-nighter tonight.

22:00.652 --> 22:03.488
That doesn't matter, but I have to drive.

22:03.947 --> 22:05.365
- I see.
- I'll give you a ride home.

22:07.451 --> 22:09.494
No, I'll take the subway.

22:13.498 --> 22:14.583
Well,

22:15.083 --> 22:18.337
we might run into my mom.
We have to be careful.

22:19.338 --> 22:20.672
And...

22:20.922 --> 22:23.050
it's such a nuisance
since you have to drive all the way

22:23.133 --> 22:24.634
back to work after dropping me off.

22:24.801 --> 22:26.344
And it's not even late, so don't worry.

22:31.016 --> 22:32.601
Is there something you're not telling me?

22:32.684 --> 22:33.894
Not at all!

22:35.812 --> 22:36.730
Why?

22:39.107 --> 22:40.650
Why would I hide anything from you?

22:41.610 --> 22:44.237
Besides, it's not like you can't tell
when I hide something from you.

22:47.115 --> 22:48.825
Right, I can tell.

23:04.257 --> 23:05.509
Just take a taxi.

23:05.926 --> 23:07.344
The subway is more convenient.

23:07.719 --> 23:10.138
- You're so stubborn.
- Let me have my way, will you?

23:10.347 --> 23:11.598
I always do.

23:13.892 --> 23:14.768
No.

23:15.685 --> 23:17.312
No one's looking. And who cares?

23:17.562 --> 23:18.563
Stop it.

23:20.190 --> 23:21.566
As soon as you get home--

23:21.691 --> 23:23.693
Yes, I'll call you. All right.

23:30.033 --> 23:31.076
Get home safely.

24:04.651 --> 24:05.777
You're still here.

24:06.945 --> 24:09.114
Do you know how many years
I've been commuting by subway?

24:09.197 --> 24:10.657
I can go home with my eyes closed.

24:12.284 --> 24:14.578
Take my phone.
I'll call you from my work phone.

24:15.745 --> 24:16.913
Seriously...

24:18.206 --> 24:19.541
That way, I won't worry.

24:24.171 --> 24:25.338
But what if Gyeong-seon calls?

24:26.047 --> 24:27.215
Just don't answer it.

24:28.425 --> 24:31.469
Well, you can just turn it off
after talking to me if you're worried.

24:32.262 --> 24:33.597
Then what if a girl calls?

24:34.514 --> 24:36.141
Do you think I'm an amateur?

24:36.516 --> 24:38.226
I've already told everyone not to call.

24:38.476 --> 24:41.563
Really? Then I'll delete
every single girl's number on your phone.

24:43.106 --> 24:44.691
Wait, give me back my phone for a second.

24:45.358 --> 24:46.693
- You've lost your chance.
- What?

24:47.319 --> 24:49.529
- Give it back.
- I'm curious to see how many there are.

25:12.969 --> 25:13.845
Bye.

27:54.506 --> 27:56.049
Why did we stop?

28:04.391 --> 28:05.392
Let's go.

28:19.614 --> 28:21.825
- Did you just take a photo of me?
- No.

28:23.576 --> 28:24.702
Give me your phone.

28:25.495 --> 28:26.871
What do you want my phone for?

28:27.288 --> 28:28.873
Give it to me before I beat you up.

28:29.374 --> 28:31.000
Did you use to be a bully?

28:31.251 --> 28:32.794
Stop joking and give me your phone.

28:32.877 --> 28:34.254
I know you took a photo.

28:34.337 --> 28:36.881
Why would I take a photo of you drooling?

28:41.594 --> 28:42.846
If you upload that photo,

28:42.929 --> 28:45.849
you'll go to jail for defamation
and violating my right of publicity.

28:46.307 --> 28:48.643
My gosh,
no one will be interested in it anyway.

28:48.935 --> 28:50.478
You must think you're really pretty.

28:51.521 --> 28:54.691
You'd better start treating me
with respect since I'm older.

28:57.360 --> 28:59.446
I keep using my age
to my benefit, don't I?

29:00.280 --> 29:01.448
I'm glad you know.

29:02.240 --> 29:04.701
I can only act this way around you.

29:06.745 --> 29:07.787
Thanks for today.

29:08.663 --> 29:10.582
I'll treat you to a meal when I have time.

29:10.665 --> 29:11.916
See you.

29:35.398 --> 29:37.108
Why did I act like such an idiot?

29:38.443 --> 29:40.445
I want to erase all those memories
from my brain!

29:42.614 --> 29:43.615
I'm an idiot.

29:51.289 --> 29:54.584
You've been through a lot of heartache
because of me.

29:55.418 --> 29:56.461
Yes, I have.

29:57.003 --> 29:59.005
You always do the things
that I tell you not to do.

30:00.548 --> 30:02.634
I'm not that bad--

30:02.717 --> 30:04.052
You always think and worry

30:04.928 --> 30:06.763
about something
that hasn't even happened yet

30:07.347 --> 30:08.431
and put yourself down.

30:09.474 --> 30:11.518
So you think
that I only do such stupid things?

30:13.353 --> 30:14.646
But why do I still like you?

30:16.397 --> 30:19.651
Because you've fallen
for my irresistible charm?

30:20.360 --> 30:22.529
- Bye.
- Hello?

30:23.863 --> 30:24.906
What...

30:25.532 --> 30:27.033
What? He actually hung up on me.

30:27.116 --> 30:30.537
My gosh, I can't believe he did that.

30:31.037 --> 30:31.913
SISTER

30:33.915 --> 30:35.041
What should I do?

30:48.012 --> 30:49.013
Yes.

30:50.431 --> 30:51.516
Hello?

30:52.684 --> 30:55.562
- It's me. You can talk.
- How did you know that it was me?

30:57.021 --> 30:57.981
Gyeong-seon?

30:58.064 --> 31:01.150
Look at you.
Who were you flirting with this time?

31:02.777 --> 31:04.904
Seung-cheol called me at work
a few minutes ago.

31:05.029 --> 31:06.197
I thought it was him again.

31:06.865 --> 31:08.032
You should be careful.

31:08.157 --> 31:09.367
There's another one

31:09.450 --> 31:11.160
who has a crush on you
besides Kang Se-yeong.

31:11.828 --> 31:12.996
That's no news to me.

31:13.997 --> 31:16.124
Every lady in this building
has a crush on me.

31:16.583 --> 31:18.543
That's not true. Jin-a doesn't.

31:22.005 --> 31:24.632
Right, she's the only exception.

31:24.924 --> 31:26.926
By the way,
why didn't you pick up your cell phone?

31:27.176 --> 31:28.970
That's why I called you at work.

31:30.221 --> 31:31.639
I guess I left it somewhere.

31:32.557 --> 31:33.975
It's probably in the meeting room.

31:35.059 --> 31:37.103
I don't expect you to be sweet to me.

31:37.186 --> 31:39.564
At least answer my calls
and let me know that you're alive.

31:39.814 --> 31:42.734
All right. Stay alive until I get home.

31:43.568 --> 31:44.986
I'll try.

31:49.073 --> 31:50.742
Gosh, that totally startled me.

31:54.579 --> 31:55.747
Did Jin-a...

32:05.214 --> 32:07.884
Look at that. She follows my advice
on things like this.

32:15.725 --> 32:18.728
I feel like they'll know who wrote what
even if we submit it anonymously.

32:19.562 --> 32:20.772
I think so too.

32:22.065 --> 32:25.276
Do you think it'll really be okay
to write the assailant's name?

32:26.945 --> 32:29.322
I guess it means we won't have to face
any consequences.

32:54.263 --> 32:56.766
EMPLOYEE SATISFACTION
AND WORKPLACE DISCRIMINATION SURVEY

33:48.484 --> 33:50.653
GOLF LESSON: HOW TO GET OUT
OF THE BUNKER EASILY

33:56.492 --> 33:58.661
MY DELICIOUS LIFE

34:18.890 --> 34:21.309
Why are we doing this all of a sudden?

34:22.685 --> 34:25.813
You can't say that.
You're the one who instigated all this.

34:25.980 --> 34:27.023
Goodbye.

34:27.106 --> 34:29.817
I was just trying to hint
that they should know when to stop

34:29.901 --> 34:32.403
since they were constantly
crossing the line.

34:32.862 --> 34:34.405
Still, it all started with you.

34:35.323 --> 34:38.076
What matters is
whether you're going to become a hero

34:38.201 --> 34:39.786
or a rebel after this.

34:40.953 --> 34:44.624
I guess that means I'm the one
to blame for whatever happens.

34:47.085 --> 34:48.377
By the way,

34:49.045 --> 34:51.756
you're awfully close
with Bo-ra these days.

34:51.839 --> 34:53.382
I heard you guys even went on a trip.

34:53.883 --> 34:57.011
Did you promise her
that you'll set her up with Jun-hui?

34:57.637 --> 34:59.972
Gosh, it was just a spontaneous getaway.

35:00.056 --> 35:01.808
Why did you have to go with her?

35:01.891 --> 35:04.143
You guys were never that close.

35:05.895 --> 35:07.271
Calm down.

35:08.147 --> 35:12.777
I have no intention to meddle in
other people's relationships.

35:13.152 --> 35:15.988
Even if you did,
it wouldn't have been of much help.

35:16.405 --> 35:18.991
Remember how I thought about
asking you to help me out?

35:20.034 --> 35:21.869
Jun-hui's older sister told me

35:22.912 --> 35:25.456
that their parents care a lot
about the other person's background.

35:26.249 --> 35:29.335
They want him to date
someone from a prestigious family.

35:30.211 --> 35:33.339
I didn't really care much,
but it still wasn't pleasant to hear.

35:33.756 --> 35:36.092
Are they from a really rich family
or something?

35:37.426 --> 35:39.053
What do their parents do?

35:40.930 --> 35:43.850
I don't know. I'm curious too.

35:50.189 --> 35:52.900
It's late.
Where are you going at this hour?

35:52.984 --> 35:54.902
Why aren't you answering me?

35:54.986 --> 35:56.988
- Tell me.
- I'll tell you when I get back.

35:57.071 --> 35:58.906
Why can't you tell me now?

35:58.990 --> 36:00.950
You act as if you're off
to do something grand.

36:03.327 --> 36:05.246
Are you going to be late?

36:08.791 --> 36:12.044
Call me if you're going to come home late.

36:21.345 --> 36:22.471
Call me.

36:55.504 --> 36:57.089
Welcome.

37:13.105 --> 37:16.234
The guy you've been describing...
Are you talking about Jun-hui?

37:17.401 --> 37:19.987
I don't know what his name is.

37:20.905 --> 37:23.074
He's Seung-ho's friend,
the guy I met at your place.

37:24.242 --> 37:25.409
He's Jin-a's boyfriend,

37:25.493 --> 37:28.162
and I heard it directly from Jin-a.

37:53.437 --> 37:55.356
- Bye.
- See you.

37:55.439 --> 37:56.482
Bye.

38:03.406 --> 38:04.448
What are you doing here?

38:05.491 --> 38:06.575
You know why I'm here.

38:07.994 --> 38:10.246
You know you are not in a position
to talk to me like that,

38:11.080 --> 38:12.206
don't you?

38:15.543 --> 38:16.585
Are we going to talk here?

38:27.013 --> 38:28.180
So, what's your point?

38:29.473 --> 38:31.642
Why did you want to see me?

38:34.061 --> 38:36.314
I want your apology.

38:37.606 --> 38:40.359
You treated me like
I was the only one at fault.

38:40.818 --> 38:42.320
I want you to apologize to me for that.

38:48.200 --> 38:49.076
I do not think

38:49.910 --> 38:51.620
I owe you an apology.

38:51.954 --> 38:55.416
You heard me.
Jin-a has been seeing someone else too.

38:55.499 --> 38:56.917
But you cheated on her first.

38:57.877 --> 39:02.340
- She has every right to date someone else.
- Well, yes. You have a point.

39:03.215 --> 39:05.343
But she's dating her brother's friend.

39:05.426 --> 39:07.345
Are you okay with that?

39:08.179 --> 39:09.347
I'm actually happy for them.

39:11.891 --> 39:15.061
I've known him since he was little,
so he's like a son to me.

39:15.978 --> 39:18.981
And I know how diligent and kind he is.

39:20.107 --> 39:22.234
So I'm more than happy that a guy like him

39:22.485 --> 39:23.819
is Jin-a's boyfriend.

39:27.782 --> 39:29.992
We always treated him like family,

39:30.659 --> 39:34.038
so Jin-a must've kept it a secret
because she didn't want to startle us.

39:35.206 --> 39:37.666
Thank you for coming all the way here

39:39.293 --> 39:40.503
to tell me the news.

43:08.544 --> 43:13.799
Are you getting a kick out of this?
Why are you all quiet? Where are you?

43:15.676 --> 43:17.094
Where are you?

43:17.970 --> 43:19.263
Why aren't you answering me?

43:20.306 --> 43:21.807
I'm with a friend.

43:23.559 --> 43:25.811
- I didn't drink a lot.
- Come home soon.

43:26.270 --> 43:28.480
Well, I'm going to sleep
at the office tonight.

43:29.356 --> 43:30.566
Don't goof around and work.

43:30.816 --> 43:31.817
All right.

43:32.192 --> 43:33.360
Good night.

43:42.786 --> 43:46.498
You'd better answer me honestly
without leaving out any details.

43:49.627 --> 43:51.629
I wouldn't have come here
if I wasn't going to do so.

43:53.672 --> 43:54.798
When did it start?

43:56.759 --> 43:58.260
Why is that important?

43:59.511 --> 44:00.888
Just answer my question.

44:00.971 --> 44:02.598
You have no right to talk back to me.

44:05.643 --> 44:06.977
What did I do wrong?

44:08.479 --> 44:09.688
Dating your older sister?

44:10.314 --> 44:11.857
Would it have been okay if I were older?

44:12.858 --> 44:14.526
You're against it because it's me.

44:15.277 --> 44:16.528
You just can't approve of me.

44:17.905 --> 44:19.239
What's your reason?

44:20.407 --> 44:21.575
Don't you know the reason?

44:22.993 --> 44:23.827
No, I don't.

44:24.411 --> 44:25.579
Are you out of your mind?

44:26.455 --> 44:28.499
Don't you know what you mean
to my parents?

44:29.750 --> 44:30.834
What do I mean to them?

44:33.671 --> 44:34.838
A son.

44:36.340 --> 44:37.341
Listen, you idiot.

44:38.342 --> 44:39.843
What's Jin-a to my parents?

44:42.304 --> 44:43.263
She's their daughter.

44:43.764 --> 44:45.474
Then let me ask you this.

44:46.433 --> 44:47.685
What about Gyeong-seon?

44:49.561 --> 44:51.730
It doesn't matter
whether you two aren't related by blood

44:51.814 --> 44:53.690
or it's not legally wrong
for you to be together.

44:54.775 --> 44:56.777
Why does it have to be Jin-a?

44:57.486 --> 44:58.946
You can easily date someone else.

44:59.613 --> 45:02.574
There are so many women around you.
Why does it have to be my sister?

45:03.992 --> 45:05.994
- Because it's Jin-a.
- Gosh.

45:06.912 --> 45:08.038
Are you joking with me now?

45:11.041 --> 45:12.292
Do I look like I'm joking?

45:14.628 --> 45:17.506
Fine. Try all you want, but just know
that you two can't be together.

45:22.052 --> 45:24.972
I won't give up
no matter what you say or do.

45:27.057 --> 45:28.809
I absolutely can't give up on Jin-a.

45:29.810 --> 45:31.061
I came here to tell you that.

45:33.063 --> 45:34.064
Hey.

45:34.898 --> 45:36.775
Do you think Gyeong-seon
will be okay with it?

45:37.067 --> 45:38.527
Do you think she'll approve of it?

45:39.611 --> 45:42.364
- If she doesn't, it is what it is.
- My gosh.

45:42.781 --> 45:44.825
You've completely lost your mind.

45:45.742 --> 45:47.077
What are you guys going to do now?

45:50.789 --> 45:52.040
Are you worried about us?

45:52.708 --> 45:54.501
Cut the crap, you nutjob.

45:59.798 --> 46:03.051
You can lose it and go bonkers.
Just take it all out on me, not her.

46:07.514 --> 46:09.057
Do me a favor, please.

46:11.059 --> 46:13.520
Don't give her a hard time.

46:43.926 --> 46:45.093
Are you going back to school--

46:45.719 --> 46:46.762
Gosh, dude.

46:48.639 --> 46:50.933
Let's go to a quiet place
if you're going to punch me.

46:52.643 --> 46:53.727
You nutjob.

46:55.479 --> 46:58.482
I swear I'm going to kill you
if you break Jin-a's heart.

47:00.484 --> 47:02.027
That will never happen.

47:02.694 --> 47:04.863
Don't laugh, you prick.
Do you want to get punched?

47:05.614 --> 47:06.657
No.

47:07.783 --> 47:09.409
Gosh, that nutjob...

47:10.536 --> 47:12.496
Seung-ho, wait up.

47:12.871 --> 47:13.705
Hey.

47:16.166 --> 47:17.042
Oh, no.

47:19.127 --> 47:20.837
- Your mom must have sent you.
- Yes, she did.

47:21.129 --> 47:24.049
I called because he drank a lot
by himself.

47:24.925 --> 47:25.842
My gosh.

47:27.928 --> 47:29.555
- Dad.
- Oh, my.

47:29.638 --> 47:30.472
Dad!

47:31.014 --> 47:32.432
- Yes?
- You've been drinking alone?

47:32.516 --> 47:34.851
Come on, wake up.

47:35.060 --> 47:37.229
- It's my daughter.
- Why did you drink so much?

47:37.479 --> 47:38.772
Why are you sleeping here?

47:39.731 --> 47:40.941
Let's go home.

47:47.948 --> 47:50.117
- Did something happen?
- What's the matter, Dad?

47:51.702 --> 47:54.162
- What's wrong?
- Nothing. I'm just...

47:55.998 --> 47:57.874
I'm just happy, that's all.

47:59.001 --> 48:00.168
My daughter...

48:01.587 --> 48:04.631
I'm so happy to see my daughters.

48:05.173 --> 48:06.466
- I'm...
- Gosh.

48:07.759 --> 48:08.885
I'm so...

48:09.970 --> 48:13.682
Okay, I heard you. Let's go home now.
Mom will nag you like crazy again.

48:13.890 --> 48:15.183
Gosh, seriously.

48:16.643 --> 48:18.395
Did you finish three bottles by yourself?

48:18.979 --> 48:20.105
Be careful.

48:21.857 --> 48:23.525
- I'm fine.
- Be careful.

48:23.859 --> 48:25.736
- You should put your jacket on first.
- Okay.

48:33.243 --> 48:35.245
That drunkard, he kills me.

48:35.871 --> 48:37.998
- Dad.
- Tell me

48:38.081 --> 48:40.459
I can't tell
whether he's in a good mood or not.

48:40.584 --> 48:42.878
- Gosh, Dad.
- What I should do

48:42.961 --> 48:45.797
You drunkard. Have you lost your mind?

48:45.881 --> 48:47.633
What the heck are you doing at this hour?

48:49.551 --> 48:51.678
My wife!

48:51.762 --> 48:53.513
Gosh, you reek of alcohol.

48:53.597 --> 48:55.932
How much did you drink?

48:56.058 --> 48:58.727
- Goodness. Stand up straight.
- Mi-yeon!

49:00.020 --> 49:01.063
I'll...

49:03.482 --> 49:06.985
- I'll be good to you.
- Gosh.

49:07.069 --> 49:09.112
I'm telling you.

49:09.988 --> 49:11.907
I'll be very good to you, okay?

49:11.990 --> 49:13.158
Stop it.

49:13.241 --> 49:14.910
He drank by himself.

49:14.993 --> 49:17.079
- Gosh, he'll fall. Mr. Yoon, wait up.
- Tell me

49:17.204 --> 49:20.290
- What's with him?
- What I should do

49:20.374 --> 49:22.167
Where did he go today?

49:22.250 --> 49:24.586
- He didn't tell me anything.
- Tell me

49:24.670 --> 49:26.546
Who the heck did he meet?
He really kills me.

49:26.630 --> 49:30.592
- What I should do
- Gosh, what's up with him today?

49:35.972 --> 49:37.432
Yes, come in.

49:44.981 --> 49:47.859
I confirmed that there is a survey
going around for the female employees.

49:48.193 --> 49:50.570
But the results haven't been submitted
to Mr. Jo yet.

49:53.990 --> 49:55.283
Why did you have to...

49:55.784 --> 49:57.160
My gosh.

49:58.245 --> 50:00.622
You see, you should really try
not to cross the line

50:00.997 --> 50:03.667
whether during a team dinner
or whatever else.

50:04.376 --> 50:07.504
All employees should respect each other.
Wouldn't that be ideal?

50:08.797 --> 50:11.007
You cross the line every time you drink.

50:12.968 --> 50:15.762
Are you incapable
of holding yourself back?

50:18.140 --> 50:21.101
About the business trip too.
I specifically asked you, didn't I?

50:22.310 --> 50:24.396
All you had to do was
give them an impression

50:25.439 --> 50:27.607
that we care for them
since they are my relatives.

50:28.775 --> 50:32.279
You should've just had a meal together
and said nice things to flatter them.

50:33.739 --> 50:35.157
I told you numerous times.

50:36.450 --> 50:39.077
- Well, that was--
- What are you going to do now?

50:41.747 --> 50:45.917
Mr. Nam, I won't make excuses
for other things,

50:46.042 --> 50:49.212
but about the business trip...
I treated Ms. Yoon like that

50:49.296 --> 50:51.173
because you told me
to take them out for a drink.

50:52.382 --> 50:53.925
Stop putting words in my mouth.

50:55.761 --> 50:58.722
Did I tell you to bring Ms. Yoon with you?

50:59.765 --> 51:02.684
I never even mentioned her name.

51:02.768 --> 51:04.352
What the hell are you talking about?

51:09.024 --> 51:10.692
How are things with the female employees?

51:12.277 --> 51:15.197
They seem a bit confused
as this has never happened before.

51:17.282 --> 51:19.493
Then I guess we can't expect
credible results.

51:19.576 --> 51:23.079
There are some who are trying
to voice their opinions.

51:23.955 --> 51:25.165
Like you are?

51:28.460 --> 51:31.129
I've only been a bystander all along.

51:32.172 --> 51:33.924
I value your opinion more than others'.

51:36.384 --> 51:37.427
It's an honor, sir.

51:44.810 --> 51:46.937
Hi. Any luck today?

51:47.979 --> 51:49.898
Wow, is that true?

51:50.899 --> 51:52.776
I'll have to fish there sometime.

52:21.012 --> 52:22.848
Enjoying a fancy dinner?

52:23.682 --> 52:25.851
I guess I pay you more than enough.

52:26.852 --> 52:29.688
Well, it's...

52:41.116 --> 52:42.993
Mr. Kong, is something bothering you?

52:43.076 --> 52:44.077
Yes.

52:45.787 --> 52:47.205
Oh, nothing.

52:48.790 --> 52:50.125
- Dong-u.
- Yes?

52:50.292 --> 52:53.295
Did you hear anything
from the female employees?

52:54.087 --> 52:55.171
Didn't you know?

52:55.505 --> 52:58.633
They don't even make eye contact
with male employees these days.

53:01.511 --> 53:02.512
Okay.

53:23.199 --> 53:24.409
Well...

53:24.492 --> 53:28.246
After work,

53:28.538 --> 53:29.915
how about we have dinner together?

53:31.583 --> 53:32.876
Good.

53:35.879 --> 53:37.005
Why did he show up?

53:37.589 --> 53:39.257
He wants to buy me dinner.

53:40.926 --> 53:43.178
So you'll have dinner with him?

53:43.261 --> 53:46.431
It seems like
he wants to tell me something.

53:46.973 --> 53:48.058
Tell you what?

53:48.516 --> 53:50.560
Say no. Turn him down.

53:51.269 --> 53:53.271
I can't do that.

53:54.481 --> 53:56.858
Why are you getting upset?

53:57.359 --> 53:59.861
How can I not be when you're having
dinner with that pervert?

54:00.153 --> 54:03.281
Okay. I'll get it over with quickly.

54:04.240 --> 54:06.326
Why can't you just tell me you won't go?

54:06.409 --> 54:07.911
You really don't listen to me.

54:08.912 --> 54:10.205
But don't go somewhere too far.

54:10.372 --> 54:12.165
Send me the address when you get there.

54:12.415 --> 54:14.000
I don't have a phone.

54:15.961 --> 54:17.837
Okay, I'll figure something out.

54:18.588 --> 54:21.007
That's why I told you I'll buy you one.

54:21.091 --> 54:25.095
You're at it again.

54:26.054 --> 54:27.889
I get it.

54:28.890 --> 54:29.933
Okay.

54:30.934 --> 54:32.477
My goodness.

54:40.819 --> 54:43.029
I should definitely buy you a meal.

54:43.113 --> 54:45.615
- Go on, help yourself.
- Yes, sir.

54:45.865 --> 54:48.493
- You should have some too, Mr. Kong.
- Okay.

54:54.040 --> 54:55.542
Aren't you going to have a drink?

54:56.167 --> 54:59.337
Would you like some, Ms. Yoon?

54:59.421 --> 55:02.382
No, sir. I was only asking about you.

55:03.216 --> 55:05.635
I don't really feel like drinking.

55:09.180 --> 55:11.224
- Here. Have this.
- Thank you.

55:14.561 --> 55:18.356
Well, did Mr. Nam send you here?

55:19.524 --> 55:21.192
No, not at all.

55:21.693 --> 55:23.486
I've always wanted

55:24.195 --> 55:26.489
to treat you to a nice meal

55:26.573 --> 55:28.324
and I finally found the time today.

55:28.616 --> 55:31.286
And you worked really hard

55:31.411 --> 55:34.205
when we went on that business trip.
That's why.

55:39.294 --> 55:40.336
Well...

55:42.005 --> 55:43.131
Yes, sir.

55:43.214 --> 55:44.507
It's just that...

55:46.426 --> 55:49.220
There is a survey going around
only for female employees, did you know?

55:51.014 --> 55:53.516
Yes, sir. I got one too.

55:55.518 --> 55:59.105
I see. Did you write anything?

56:00.190 --> 56:03.276
I don't think I'm going to.

56:06.529 --> 56:08.198
Since there are too many things to write,

56:09.032 --> 56:11.076
and I'm not good at putting
my thoughts down on paper,

56:11.868 --> 56:13.495
I'm considering reporting things verbally.

56:33.139 --> 56:35.517
- Excuse me. I have to use the restroom.
- Sure.

56:35.600 --> 56:37.393
- Are you ready to order?
- This will get burnt.

56:37.477 --> 56:38.394
Excuse me.

56:59.499 --> 57:01.292
Were you that worried about me?

57:02.293 --> 57:03.628
You didn't have to come.

57:04.462 --> 57:07.632
Then why did you send me the address
and the phone number of this place?

57:10.301 --> 57:13.221
- I came because I missed you.
- Too late.

57:14.305 --> 57:15.723
I'll sit next to you in there.

57:15.974 --> 57:17.058
What?

57:17.392 --> 57:19.727
Stop fooling around.

57:20.437 --> 57:24.107
I can't stand him
sitting right across from you.

57:24.232 --> 57:26.693
I'm going to get out of there soon.
Be patient.

57:28.528 --> 57:29.529
I'll think about it.

57:31.573 --> 57:34.659
You'd better listen to me
while I ask nicely.

57:38.621 --> 57:39.998
Gosh.

57:48.256 --> 57:50.341
Thank you for the dinner, sir.

57:50.425 --> 57:52.260
It's nothing.

57:52.427 --> 57:54.888
I'll treat you to something
better and fancier next time.

57:54.971 --> 57:56.764
You don't have to.

57:57.557 --> 58:00.477
I don't feel comfortable,
and this is more than enough.

58:02.103 --> 58:03.229
Ms. Yoon.

58:06.024 --> 58:09.402
I am in a position
where I have to consider other people,

58:09.486 --> 58:12.447
and I can't take sides.

58:13.781 --> 58:15.700
So if...

58:17.785 --> 58:21.456
If I have ever disappointed you
in any way,

58:21.539 --> 58:23.374
please try to understand my situation.

58:23.666 --> 58:25.460
Feel free to confront me
whenever you need to.

58:28.171 --> 58:32.675
I'm a bit taken aback
as I didn't expect you to tell me this.

58:33.301 --> 58:37.388
Talking about unexpected change,
you've changed a lot.

58:37.472 --> 58:39.432
I'm not the only one who feels this way.

58:39.516 --> 58:41.518
It's like you're a different person
these days.

58:41.643 --> 58:42.936
Didn't anyone say this to you?

58:45.146 --> 58:47.106
Some people did.

58:47.190 --> 58:48.566
See?

58:48.650 --> 58:50.401
While we're on the subject, tell me.

58:51.110 --> 58:53.821
Why did you change so suddenly?

58:57.534 --> 59:00.578
I wanted to help someone.

59:05.708 --> 59:08.294
All this time,

59:09.504 --> 59:12.757
I didn't realize my worth.

59:13.383 --> 59:17.679
But I met someone who treasures me

59:18.513 --> 59:20.598
more than I treasure myself

59:21.474 --> 59:23.476
and tries to protect me.

59:24.310 --> 59:26.896
And I decided to help that person.

59:28.815 --> 59:31.609
I should care for myself

59:32.360 --> 59:33.861
so that that person would worry less

59:34.320 --> 59:38.449
and feel at ease.

59:59.512 --> 01:00:02.265
I used your phone for a bit.

01:00:02.390 --> 01:00:03.725
Mine is broken, you know.

01:00:04.392 --> 01:00:06.603
You should get it repaired
or buy a new one.

01:00:06.686 --> 01:00:08.062
I will get one soon.

01:00:10.773 --> 01:00:14.485
Are you okay? I heard you were in bed
all day because you were hungover.

01:00:14.569 --> 01:00:15.820
I'm better now.

01:00:16.863 --> 01:00:18.573
That's a relief.

01:00:19.365 --> 01:00:21.367
Is there anything you want to tell me?

01:00:21.993 --> 01:00:22.994
No.

01:00:24.996 --> 01:00:26.873
You can tell me anything.

01:00:26.998 --> 01:00:30.376
I'm ready to listen whatever it may be.

01:00:31.794 --> 01:00:33.463
You don't need to get yourself ready
for it.

01:00:34.172 --> 01:00:36.466
I asked you last time

01:00:37.759 --> 01:00:39.385
to wait a little longer.

01:00:39.802 --> 01:00:40.887
For now,

01:00:42.430 --> 01:00:43.556
that's all I can say to you.

01:00:44.974 --> 01:00:47.560
Okay. Talk to me when you want to.

01:00:52.523 --> 01:00:53.691
I'll go to my room.

01:01:22.679 --> 01:01:24.180
What should I do?

01:01:31.979 --> 01:01:32.980
Oh, my.

01:01:33.940 --> 01:01:35.274
My goodness.

01:01:53.710 --> 01:01:54.919
Why are you going that way?

01:01:55.586 --> 01:01:57.588
There's a store at the intersection.

01:01:57.714 --> 01:01:59.340
I need to take my car.

01:02:19.318 --> 01:02:20.486
If it weren't...

01:02:21.904 --> 01:02:23.906
If it weren't for the account transfer
of your phone,

01:02:25.283 --> 01:02:26.784
you wouldn't have called me, would you?

01:02:28.745 --> 01:02:31.372
- Isn't that the normal thing to do?
- Why?

01:02:31.998 --> 01:02:34.083
Because your young boyfriend
might get jealous?

01:02:37.336 --> 01:02:38.796
Don't bring him up.

01:02:38.880 --> 01:02:40.965
Gosh, why can't I even talk about him?

01:02:43.468 --> 01:02:45.845
What's so great about him?

01:02:46.471 --> 01:02:47.722
Is he from a rich family?

01:02:49.515 --> 01:02:52.894
Of all the guys you could've met,
how could you date your brother's friend?

01:02:54.687 --> 01:02:56.189
The store will close soon.

01:02:56.272 --> 01:02:58.733
I really need to get this done
as soon as possible, so let's go.

01:03:22.965 --> 01:03:24.008
Jun-hui.

01:03:39.440 --> 01:03:40.525
Jun-hui.

01:03:42.735 --> 01:03:44.529
Jun-hui, it's me.

01:03:46.864 --> 01:03:48.908
I just wanted to record you something

01:03:49.784 --> 01:03:52.662
since I have your phone with me.

01:03:54.956 --> 01:03:56.040
Thank you.

01:03:58.376 --> 01:04:02.421
Thank you for caring about me
and loving me.

01:04:04.257 --> 01:04:05.883
I didn't know

01:04:06.968 --> 01:04:09.887
that I could be loved so much by someone.

01:04:11.973 --> 01:04:13.641
You probably don't know

01:04:14.559 --> 01:04:18.062
how grateful and happy I am

01:04:18.896 --> 01:04:21.190
these days.

01:04:24.443 --> 01:04:26.529
I'm also learning a lot from you.

01:04:27.572 --> 01:04:28.865
I learned

01:04:30.741 --> 01:04:33.202
that love is about giving your all

01:04:34.620 --> 01:04:36.497
to that one special person

01:04:37.123 --> 01:04:39.834
to the best of your abilities.

01:04:42.587 --> 01:04:46.090
That's why when someone's in love,

01:04:47.675 --> 01:04:48.926
they should love like you do.

01:04:51.012 --> 01:04:52.096
Jun-hui.

01:04:55.892 --> 01:04:57.018
I love you

01:04:59.604 --> 01:05:00.897
with all my heart.

01:05:03.149 --> 01:05:06.152
I will love you for a long time.

01:05:34.263 --> 01:05:35.765
Where are we going?

01:05:37.224 --> 01:05:38.517
Tell me where we are going!

01:05:57.745 --> 01:05:58.579
Hey.

01:06:17.014 --> 01:06:18.015
Jun-hui.

01:06:20.226 --> 01:06:22.019
Jun-hui, it's me.

01:06:31.779 --> 01:06:33.990
Hey, what are you doing?

01:06:35.074 --> 01:06:36.283
Have you lost your mind?

01:06:37.159 --> 01:06:38.411
Stop the car.

01:06:39.120 --> 01:06:40.329
Stop the car right now!

01:07:54.570 --> 01:07:55.780
Don't do this.

01:07:56.655 --> 01:08:00.159
Gyu-min, please don't do this.

01:08:02.912 --> 01:08:05.623
What are you trying to do?

01:08:06.040 --> 01:08:07.625
What do you want?

01:08:08.751 --> 01:08:09.835
I'm going to die.

01:08:11.587 --> 01:08:13.672
I'm going to die with you.

01:08:17.093 --> 01:08:19.136
Come on, move. Move.

01:08:19.929 --> 01:08:21.138
Get out of the way.

01:08:55.005 --> 01:08:57.800
I was sure that something had happened.

01:08:57.883 --> 01:09:01.303
- I hoped that I'd be wrong.
- Jin-a, where are you right now?

01:09:01.387 --> 01:09:02.680
I regretted it so much.

01:09:02.805 --> 01:09:05.891
I should've gone to pick you up.
I shouldn't have left you alone.

01:09:05.975 --> 01:09:08.477
Honestly, imagine if it were us.

01:09:08.561 --> 01:09:10.312
Will you let Jin-a marry into that family?

01:09:10.813 --> 01:09:13.774
I don't want to hide our relationship
anymore.

01:09:14.191 --> 01:09:15.860
Let's make it public before we get caught.

01:09:16.735 --> 01:09:19.321
I'm here to meet my boyfriend.

01:09:19.822 --> 01:09:20.656
Oh, I see.

01:09:20.739 --> 01:09:22.449
I'm dating Jun-hui.

01:09:22.533 --> 01:09:23.492
I couldn't stop.

01:09:23.576 --> 01:09:25.995
Go kill yourself! I'm really sorry.

01:09:26.078 --> 01:09:27.413
You must be very happy.

01:09:28.164 --> 01:09:30.624
- I really am. It's almost intimidating.
- Stop it.

01:09:30.708 --> 01:09:34.211
If I keep hiding behind you,
she'll be even more disappointed in me.

01:09:34.503 --> 01:09:35.671
I'll love you longer,

01:09:37.339 --> 01:09:40.759
and I'll love you more.

01:09:43.846 --> 01:09:45.848
Subtitle translation by Choi Hyeon-ju
